Text: SEMINARIO INTERNACIONAL DE GAS Cc La Embajada Britnica en Colombia invita al Seminario Internacional de Gas que se llevar a cabo en Bogot Colombia el prximo de noviembre de acuerdo al programa adjunto Programa Seminario de Gasdoc Please note that all messages sent and received by members of the Foreign and Commonwealth Office and its missions overseas may be monitored centrally This is done to ensure the integrity of the system Programa Seminario de Gasdoc
